{"tid":2516063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《文匯報》又施壓 要求最少要民事追究東方昇","createTime":"2021-05-04T11:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:42:08.000Z","uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4df67a76322683870355e6011da8e019e548955c","tid":2516063,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1567428860126676/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1567428860126676%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=431e3793\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1567428860126676/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNa9Ygt1eEmZD5kJxBvuaBkx26LN5top8F7jn52nVKmhC?filename=WZidVWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZidVWr.jpg&h=3d177bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">中共中央香港工作委員會/中聯辦附屬傳媒《文匯報》剛剛發帖，指《100毛》 東方昇於觀塘海濱公園行為猥瑣，而且影響衛生之餘，更指東方昇犯眾憎。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n犯眾憎一事明顯呼應早前工聯會所謂觀塘噴泉關注組言論，即<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">聲稱東方昇赤裸上身洗澡低俗當有趣及畫面猥瑣，使用梘液令噴泉損壞，促請康樂及文化事務署追討之餘，更指袒胸露臂行為令人不恥。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n剷屎官小編事先聲明，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">工聯會所謂民意並不代表我。</span></span>黨媒海納百川有容乃大，以前可以勸香港人包容中國人在街上不文明行為時，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港乃是多元文化社會，假若連行為藝術都不能包容，黨媒有何口氣要求香港居民包容？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論如何黨已經向黨媒「下聖旨」，東方昇的處境不得不令人擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n-📸：《文匯報》fb<br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/COcw5enAPLa/?igshid=1kqa5q8q9jfb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOcw5enAPLa%2F%3Figshid%3D1kqa5q8q9jfb4&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=ce27c6e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOcw5enAPLa%2F%3Figshid%3D1kqa5q8q9jfb4&h=3abf2f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/COcw5enAPLa/?igshid=1kqa5q8q9jfb4</a><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n希望大家支持僅有的寫作自主！<br />\nPatreon : <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/ksaviation1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fksaviation1&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=9de6ced2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/ksaviation1</a>"}]}